title: Nýlegt mix sem ég gerði fyrir Partyzone
text:
Á Soundcloud síðunni minni er hægt að nálgast nýlegt mix sem ég gerði fyrir Partyzone.
www.soundcloud.com/leopold
Takk fyrir að hlusta!
1. Marcellis - Come and Boogie (Black Label)
2. Marcel knopf - Rec-Chord (Mo's Ferry)
3. Seth Troxler - Hurt (feat. Matthew Dear) (Spectral Sound)
4. Sun Electric - Sissy (Shitkatapult)
5. Furry Phreaks & Terra Deva - Want me like water (Herbert's Tension dub) (Peacefrog)
6. Die Vögel - Petardo (Pampa)
7. Alex Celler - Ductile (Cinematic)
8. Ike - Pressin' On (Philpot)
9. Sweet Exorcist - Track Jack (Warp)
10. dOP - Cold World (Watergate)
11. Leopold Kristjansson II - Faux Pas (Affin - coming soon)
12. Detachments - Circles (Martyn's Round and Round remix) (This is not an Exit)
